T02TD3453E:110a-1: badzra aa nam ga s'a dha nam /
T02TD3453E:110a-3: yan lag med pa'i rdo rje'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD3453E:110a-5: sngon du gsungs pa'i cho gas 'dir stong pa nyid du bsgoms nas /
T02TD3453E:110a-6: sna tshogs padma dang nyi ma la pam yig ser po'i sa bon yongs su gyur pa las skad cig gis rje btsun 'jam dpal yan lag med pa'i rdo rjer bdag nyid bskyed de /
T02TD3453E:110a-7: sku mdog ser po zhal gcig pa /
T02TD3453E:110a-9: phyag drug pa ral pa'i cod pan can /
T02TD3453E:110a-10: lo brgyad gnyis lon pa lta bu sgeg pa dang bcas pa /
T02TD3453E:110a-13: me long rnams ni g-yas kyi phyag gsum na'o //
T02TD3453E:110b-0: @110b lo ma dang bcas pa'i me tog rnams ni g-yon gyi phyag gsum na bsnams pa'o //
T02TD3453E:110b-1: mdzes pa'i rgyan dang na bzas brgyan pa /
T02TD3453E:110b-2: mi bskyod pa'i cod pan can bsgoms nas /
T02TD3453E:110b-3: myos byed rab tu sbyor bar bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD3453E:110b-4: de bzhin du mnga' yis nu ma phug nas mya ngan med pa'i yal gas brdung zhing khrid nas ral gris bsgrub bya skrag cing me long de la bstan par bya'o //
T02TD3453E:110b-5: autpal gyis rkang pa bcings nas myos shing skra grol te /
T02TD3453E:110b-7: aom che ge mo a'a k'arsha ya manydzu gho sha hr'i: dza:zhes pa ni yan lag med pa'i rdo rje'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so//
